#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.210"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.210:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.210:0.2"
msgid "21. Kimilavagga"
msgstr "21. With Kimbila"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.210:0.3"
msgid "210. Muṭṭhassatisutta"
msgstr "210. Unmindful"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.210:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa niddaṃ okkamayato."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of falling asleep unmindful and "
"unaware."

msgctxt "an5.210:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.210:1.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ supati, dukkhaṃ paṭibujjhati, pāpakaṃ supinaṃ passati, devatā na "
"rakkhanti, asuci muccati."
msgstr ""
"You sleep badly and wake miserably. You have bad dreams. The deities don’t "
"protect you. And you emit semen."

msgctxt "an5.210:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa niddaṃ "
"okkamayato."
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks of falling asleep unmindful and unaware."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.210:2.1"
msgid ""
"Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā upaṭṭhitassatissa sampajānassa niddaṃ "
"okkamayato."
msgstr "There are these five benefits of falling asleep mindful and aware."

msgctxt "an5.210:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.210:2.3"
msgid ""
"Sukhaṃ supati, sukhaṃ paṭibujjhati, na pāpakaṃ supinaṃ passati, devatā "
"rakkhanti, asuci na muccati."
msgstr ""
"You sleep well and wake happily. You don’t have bad dreams. The deities "
"protect you. And you don’t emit semen."

msgctxt "an5.210:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā upaṭṭhitassatissa sampajānassa niddaṃ "
"okkamayato”ti."
msgstr "These are the five benefits of falling asleep mindful and aware.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.210:2.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.210:2.6"
msgid "Kimilavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.210:3.1"
msgid "Kimilo dhammassavanaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.210:3.2"
msgid "ājānīyo balaṃ khilaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.210:3.3"
msgid "Vinibandhaṃ yāgu kaṭṭhaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.210:3.4"
msgid "gītaṃ muṭṭhassatinā cāti."
msgstr ""
